#, no-wrap
msgid "How to open a root terminal"
msgstr "Com obrir un terminal d'administrador"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"To open a root terminal during your working session, you can do any of the "
"following:"
msgstr ""
"Per obrir un terminal d'administrador durant la sessió de treball, podeu fer "
"qualsevol de les accions següents:"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"- Choose **Applications**&nbsp;▸ **System Tools**&nbsp;▸ **Root Terminal**."
msgstr ""
"- Trieu **Aplicacions**&nbsp;▸ **Eines del sistema**&nbsp;▸ **Terminal "
"d'administrador**."

#. type: Plain text
msgid "- Execute the command `sudo -i` in a terminal."
msgstr "- Executeu l'ordre `sudo -i` en un terminal."

